snippet.title: Evergrow - Game Trailer - Out now for iOS
snippet.description:
Available now on the App Store: http://apple.co/Evergrow

Evergrow is a visually enticing game featuring fresh physics-based gameplay and fluid multi-touch mechanics, where you must help a block-like lifeform grow to become as big as possible.

http://www.evergrowgame.com
http://twitter.com/evergrowgame
http://facebook.com/evergrowgame

Trailer Music by Sabzi: http://sabzi.co
